Southern California Edison Gameshow

Description

Collaborated with an engineer at Southern California Edison to create a team building game inspired by the last round of Family Feud. The game is designed to have someone running the game and inputting the answers said by contestants. Most answers are changed to protect sensitive information of SCE employees. The top answers are in a text file downloadable below.
